freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Day 4 post vaccine I had runny nose, aches, thought I was getting a cold but symptoms vanished overnight. Day 7 they returned and I was sick for 4 days with body aches, extreme fatigue, headache ...and runny nose was only for 1-2 days. Negative test.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I have not received my daily check for 3 days. Yesterday I had runny nose and sniffles and irritated eyes, like a cold, but symptoms were gone today.

I was not given an opportunity to report before now. Night after #2 I had horrid chills. Major flu symptoms 1-2 days after injection..better day 3 after but cold-like symptoms day 4 and ache, fatigue day 5. Arm pain for 5 days after injection. Feeling almost myself on 6th day after (today)
